1. *Reci* mu da će biti sve u redu! (Tell him that everything will be okay!)
2. On je *rekao* da će se vratiti uskoro. (He said that he will be back soon.)
3. Šta mnogo *reci* o njemu? (What do you say about him?)
4. Ona nam je *recitala* svoju poeziju. (She recited her poetry to us.)
5. *Reci* nam šta misliš o tome. (Tell us what you think about it.)